Interface LazyLoadListModel<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the class of the list items
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, javax.swing.ListModel<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BeanListComboBoxModel, BeanListModel, FileSuggestModel
    public interface LazyLoadListModel<T>
extends javax.swing.ListModel<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    A list model that supports loading the list items lazily.
